buyerAgent.name: Shelly Salas Your Home Sold Guaranteed

data.description: Discover abundant space in this 4-bed, 2.5-bath home nestled in the sought-after Bridgewood neighborhood, just minutes from Ft. Cavazos military base and Killeen airport. Enjoy the convenience of a short 5-minute drive to HEB, Walmart, ALDI, and other major shopping centers. The primary bedroom is conveniently situated downstairs, with three spacious bedrooms upstairs and a versatile loft area. Delight in the expansive yard, complete with a beautifully built shed that conveys, along with sleek black kitchen appliances. The washer and dryer are also included, making this the perfect affordable haven for comfortable living. Seller is offering up to 8,000 in seller concessions to use towards closing cost.
